## /api/users

### POST

Create a user.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "user1",
            "password": "passw",
            "email": "user1@gmail.com",
            "description": "This is user1"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "username": "user1",
            "email": "user1@gmail.com",
            "description": "This is user1"
        }


