# Group Idea

Resource Define

    {
        "id": "number",
        "user_id": "number",
        "category_id": "number",
        "title": "string",
        "description": "string",
        "problem": "string",
        "solution": "string"
    }


## /api/ideas/{id}

### GET

Get the idea.

+ Parameters

    + id: `1` (number, optional)
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "user_id": 1,
            "category_id": 1,
            "title": "Fly Jacket",
            "description": "This is a jacket which enable flying",
            "problem": "People cannot fly",
            "solution": "Use Fly Jacket"
        }

### POST

Update the idea.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "title": "Awesome Flying Jacket"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "user_id": 1,
            "category_id": 1,
            "title": "Fly Jacket",
            "description": "This is a jacket which enable flying",
            "problem": "People cannot fly",
            "solution": "Use Fly Jacket"
        }


## /api/ideas{?user_id}

### GET

Get user's created ideas.

+ Parameters

    + user_id: `1` 

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "user_id": 1,
                "category_id": 1,
                "title": "Fly Jacket",
                "description": "This is a jacket which enable flying",
                "problem": "People cannot fly",
                "solution": "Use Fly Jacket"
            }
        ]

### POST

Create an idea.

+ Parameters

    + user_id: `1` (number, required)

+ Attributes

    + title (string, required)
    + category_id (number, optional)
    + description (string, required)
    + problem (string, required)
    + solution (string, required)

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "category_id": 1,
            "title": "Fly Jacket",
            "description": "This is a jacket which enable flying",
            "problem": "People cannot fly",
            "solution": "Use Fly Jacket"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "user_id": 1,
            "category_id": 1,
            "title": "Fly Jacket",
            "description": "This is a jacket which enable flying",
            "problem": "People cannot fly",
            "solution": "Use Fly Jacket"
        }
        
